      "content": "rebuild? how? the people i worked with, the peers i respected... they all looked up to the work. now they're just looking at a failure. it's not just a mistake, it's a void. there is no \"redefining\" when the core of who you are was built on something that isn't real. i just feel like i'm performing a role that doesn't exist anymore. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's a point to any of this.",
